---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/mainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Services" current_page="services">
    <div class="container mx-auto p-4 gap-2">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-2 border-l-4 pl-2 border-l-secondary">
            Bridging Tradition and Technology
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-2">
            At Valink Solutions, we are dedicated to creating a connected era that harmonizes tradition and technology. Our suite of services includes cutting-edge IT solutions, software development, and creative services tailored to meet the diverse needs of all communities.
        </p>

        <div class="card relative flex flex-col p-4 mt-6 bg-base-100">
            <div class="absolute -top-4 card bg-base-100 px-2 p-1 border-4 border-base-300">
                <h1 class=" font-bold uppercase">Our Services</h1>
            </div>

            <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-semibold border-l-4 pl-2 border-l-primary mb-2">IT Solutions</h3>
            <p>
                Harnessing cutting-edge Rust and ARM-based technologies, our IT solutions deliver reliable, secure, and scalable systems. We extend the benefits of modern technology to all communities, recognizing the significance of connectivity in today's world.
            </p>

            <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold border-l-4 pl-2 border-l-primary mb-2">Software Development</h3>
            <p>
                Our expert developers use Rust and Python to craft bespoke software solutions. From community-specific applications to tools preserving cultural knowledge, we build software aligned with values and traditions while embracing modernity.
            </p>

            <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold border-l-4 pl-2 border-l-primary mb-2">Creative Services</h3>
            <p>
                Beyond technology, our graphic design team, specializing in sports logos and digital art, offers services that celebrate cultural heritage while embracing modern aesthetics. We collaborate to ensure designs reflect tradition, creating visually compelling representations.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-l-4 pl-2 border-l-secondary">
            Community-Centric Approach
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
            At Valink Solutions, our mission extends beyond being a technology provider. We pride ourselves on being a hub of innovation and respect for tradition, actively engaging with communities, offering not just services but meaningful partnerships in the restoration of traditions and medicines. By intertwining cutting-edge technology with cultural preservation, we contribute to the broader healing journey, addressing both the technological and holistic needs of Aboriginal communities.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-semibold border-l-4 pl-2 border-l-secondary">
            Get in Touch
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
            Ready to embark on a transformative journey with us? Reach out to discuss how our services, often at reduced rates or pro bono, can benefit your community. Click the button below to contact us.
        </p>

        <button class="mt-4 bg-purple-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-purple-700">
            Contact Us
        </button>

    </div>
</MainLayout>